Package maze.gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CustomMazeDialog
    Class responsible for the display and for the procedures of the dialog of the custom maze option.
    CustomMazeDialogCharPanel
    Class responsible for the display and for the procedures of the custom maze elements on the top of the custom maze dialog.
    CustomMazeDialogMazePanel
    Class responsible for the display and for the procedures of the maze panel of the custom maze dialog,where the maze elements are inserted.
    CustomMazeSizeDialog
    Class responsible for the display and for the procedures of the dialog of the custom maze size that appears on the beginning of the configuration of the custom maze.
    GameFiles
    Class responsible for the save and load algorithms.
    GraphicPanel  
    GUI
    Class responsible for creating the frame in which all the graphic components are created and also the Menu bar on the top of the frame.
    GUIlauncher  
    InitialGamePanel
    Class responsible for the display and for the procedures of the panel that appears to configure a new game.
    initialMenuPanel  
    Main
    Class responsible for launching the graphical user interface of the game.
    mazeGUI  
    MazePanel
    Class responsible for the display and for the procedures of the panel that displays the maze structure in a graphical interface.
    MenuPanel
    Class responsible for the display and for the procedures of the initial menu that appearers in the beginning of the application.
    Options
    Class responsible for the display and for the procedures of the dialog that presents the options menu for the key configuration.
